<h1>Navbar</h1>

<h2>Basic navbar</h2>

<p>Use <code>w-nav-bar</code> tag to create a <a href="/api/havok/widget/NavBar.html">havok/widget/NavBar</a>.</p>

<p>Put a nav bar anywhere within a <code>.container</code>, which sets the width of your site and content.</p>

<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-nav-bar>
        <a class="brand">Title</a>
        <w-nav-bar-links>
            <a class="active">Home</a>
            <a>Link</a>
            <a>Link</a>
        </w-nav-bar-links>
    </w-nav-bar>
</div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set navBarExample1 %}
<w-nav-bar>
    <a class="brand">Title</a>
    <w-nav-bar-links>
        <a class="active">Home</a>
        <a>Link</a>
        <a>Link</a>
    </w-nav-bar-links>{% endset %}{{navBarExample1|e}}
</w-nav-bar>
</pre>

<h2>Navbar components</h2>

<h3>Brand</h3>
<p>A simple link to show your brand or project name only requires an anchor tag.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-nav-bar>
        <a class="brand" href="#">Title</a>
    </w-nav-bar>
</div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set navBarExample2 %}
<w-nav-bar>
    <a class="brand" href="#">Title</a>{% endset %}{{navBarExample2|e}}
</w-nav-bar>
</pre>

<h3>Nav links</h3>
<p>Nav items are simple to add via the <code>nav-bar-links</code> tag, which creates a <a href="/api/havok/widget/NavBarLinks.html">havok/widget/NavBarLinks</a> widget.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-nav-bar>
        <w-nav-bar-links>
            <a class="active">Home</a>
            <a>Link</a>
            <a>Link</a>
        </w-nav-bar-links>
    </w-nav-bar>
</div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
{% set navBarExample3 %}
<w-nav-bar>
    <w-nav-bar-links>
        <a class="active">Home</a>
        <a>Link</a>
        <a>Link</a>
    </w-nav-bar-links>
</w-nav-bar>{% endset %}{{navBarExample3|e}}
</pre>

<p>You can easily add dividers to your nav links with an empty list item and a simple class. Just use the <code>hr</code> tag.</p>
<div class="bs-docs-example">
    <w-nav-bar>
        <w-nav-bar-links>
            <a class="active">Home</a>
            <hr />
            <a>Link</a>
            <hr />
            <a>Link</a>
        </w-nav-bar-links>
    </w-nav-bar>
</div>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums">
